  "informal_statement": "For all real numbers a, b: a^2 + b^2 >= 2ab. Equivalent to (a - b)^2 >= 0.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "nlinarith with the explicit hint term sq_nonneg (a - b); nlinarith cannot synthesize this square-nonnegativity witness on its own (see the paired negative example).",
